Went to sonic today for lunch, the food was fast and accurate and who doesn't love the tator tots at sonic?
They are always perfect!!
I also really like that you can add flavors to your sodas, something you don't see very often.
I love cherry and vanilla flavors and always add one to my drink.
(Cherry to sprite today) Overall value is really good, and it satisfied me for lunch.
I was in a bit of a hurry and it was quick, like you would expect!

Went to this sonic for the first time.
