It took about 5 mins for them to take my order which is understandable because I wasn't the only one who pulled up.
So I ordered a footlong Chili cheese dog with tots and a 44oz cherry coke (my favorite).
The food came out pretty fast.
There were two girls that brought me my food.
I assume the one that actually gave me my food was the trainee.
She was nice and friendly.
So I get back to my hotel room, it's like 30 seconds away from sonic.
And I took a bite of the hot dog.
It seemed like it was not fresh.
But the cherry coke made up for it.
So I gave it 3 stars.

